rComments: He gave me an unrealistic view of university because of how good he was as a professor

Dr. Burgess took his first crack at it this past year, and I couldn't have asked for better: he conveyed the material effectively and interactively, he was always available for extra help, and he was all around pleasant. Any faculty should feel it is a privilege to have Dr. Burgess on board, and I would gladly take any class he was teaching.

He mentioned in one of his lectures, he was a prof for the first time. He is definitely one prof that shows you exactly what you're going to expect on the exam. Just note down how he does the problems and you should not have any trouble in any exams. He's pretty easy. But be ready to sleep, because sometimes he gets boring...
The class is really insightful and the assignments and midterm closely reflects what was discussed in the lectures! Fair prof! I can't believe it's made me so interested in chemistry!
This professor has truly changed my life.  I wish the classes lasted the whole day.  I will never look at chemistry the same way again.

Professor Burgess is funny, kind, and brilliant.  You got questions? He will answer it for you.  He will stay with you every step of the way until you understand.  He is also the most beautiful professor.
Lectures were clear and concise, was very helpful in explaining problems.
A truly inspirational fellow with a knack for witticisms.
